graph TD
  Start([User runs tcat]) --> Read[Read file bytes]
  Read --> Detect{Type known?}
  Detect -->|yes| Encode[Base64 encode]
  Detect -->|no| Err1[Exit 2: unknown extension]
  Encode --> Check{Within size limit?}
  Check -->|yes| Emit[Emit OSC 1338]
  Check -->|no| Err2[Exit 1: exceeds limit]
  Emit --> SmartTerm[SmartTerminal renders inline]
  Emit --> Other[Other terminals strip silently]
